~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   Command~RS  : unban                                     ~FTPODnuts
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

~FT   Usage~RS    : unban site/user <site or username>

   This command will unban either a site or a user, the name of which are
   written in the files 'siteban' and 'userban' in the 'podnuts/datafiles'
   directory.

~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+
~FT   See also~RS : ban, listbans
~FT+-----------------------------------------------------------------------------+

